@startuml
' Onboarding flow for first-run
start
:Check data directories;
if (No admin account?) then (yes)
  :Prompt create admin account;
  :Save admin credentials (hashed);
endif
:Load persona state;
:Run model bootstrap (optional);
:Show quick tour (dashboard, persona, learning requests);
:Ask to configure cloud sync & API keys;
if (Enable cloud sync?) then (yes)
  :Test cloud connection;
endif
stop
@enduml
